<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Passeck zu "Hasla" (unklar)</head><p>Der Rat versichert die Freundschaft und teilt die Bereitschaft mit, sich wegen der Verdächtigungen gegen den Adressaten bei Nennung Betroffener zu erkundigen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l23"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Poſſekon <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu haſla </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey daʒ Jr ın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l25"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> ſein ſüllet etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l26">Nu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> in ſunderheıt mıt eẅch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l27">nıht ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts / VVeſt <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr <expan>keıne<ex>n</ex></expan> der </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_208" id="103r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l1"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der eẅch in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> hett / VVenn vns <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l2">benennet <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ır red <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören vnd eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l3">ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> tun ob das an vns <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> wurd / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l4">v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Andree <expan>App<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Possekon <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu Hasla </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wie ewch
                                <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz ir in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> sein süllet etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> in sunderheit mit ewch
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht zu
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts. West <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ir <expan>keine<ex>n</ex></expan> der <pb facs="#facs_208" id="103r"/>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, der ewch in
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> hett, wenn uns
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>, die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> benennet <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ir red <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören und ewch ein
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> tun, ob das an uns
                            <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> wurd. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Andree <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
